                <div class="detail-wrapper">
                    <div class="detail-title">
                        大模型技术及趋势总结                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-data">
                        <div class="box">
                            <span>发布日期：2024-06-29 12:43:38</span>
                            <span>浏览次数： 3449</span>
                            <span>来源：白玉盘</span>                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-content">
                                                <p>
    <br>
</p>
                        <p style="margin: 10px auto;padding: 0px;text-indent: 0px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">本篇文章旨在希望大家对大模型的本质、技术和发展趋势有简单的了解。由于近期大模型技术发展很快，这里对大模型的技术、本质及未来趋势进行总结和探讨时，因为水平有限，疏漏在所难免。请大家谅解。</span></p><h1 style="margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.5;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">引言</span></h1><p style="margin: 10px auto;padding: 0px;text-indent: 0px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">大模型将成为通用人工智能的重要途径。在这个由0和1编织的数字时代，人工智能的腾飞已不是科技梦想，而是日益切实的现实。其中，大模型作为人工智能的核心力量，正以前所未有的方式重塑着我们的生活、学习和工作。无论是智能语音助手、自动驾驶汽车，还是医疗诊断系统，大模型都是幕后英雄，让这些看似不可思议的事情变为可能。</span></p><h1 style="margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.5;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">人工智能的发展历史</span></h1><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">1.<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><strong class="token bold" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">1950s-1970s：AI的诞生和早期发展</strong></span></span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">1950年，图灵测试的提出，为机器智能提供了一个评估标准。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">1956年，达特茅斯会议标志着人工智能作为一门学科的正式诞生。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">1960年代，早期的AI研究集中在逻辑推理和问题解决上。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">2.<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><strong class="token bold" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">1980s：专家系统的兴起</strong></span></span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">专家系统的成功应用，如MYCIN在医学诊断领域的应用。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">机器学习算法开始发展，如决策树和早期的神经网络。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">3.<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><strong class="token bold" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">1990s：机器学习的进展</strong></span></span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">反向传播算法的提出，极大地推动了神经网络的研究。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">1997年，IBM的深蓝击败国际象棋世界冠军，展示了AI在策略游戏中的能力。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">4.<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><strong class="token bold" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">2000s：大数据和计算能力的提升</strong></span></span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">互联网的普及带来了海量数据，为机器学习提供了丰富的训练素材。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">计算能力的提升，尤其是GPU的广泛应用，加速了深度学习的发展。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">5.<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;"><strong class="token bold" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">2010s：深度学习革命</strong></span></span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">◦<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;">2012年，AlexNet在ImageNet竞赛中的胜利，标志着深度学习在图像识别领域的突破。</span></span></div><div style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(64, 50, 38);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-